annotationA: Peroxin 10 is a peroxisome protein that is important for sperm development
annotationB: Peroxin 1 (Pex1) is a member of the family of AAA-ATPases required for peroxisome assembly. Pex1 depletion results in disorganization of neurons and glia and embryonic lethality. Larval escapers exhibit developmental delay, poor feeding and uncoordinated locomotion
